# Sentiment Curator Frontend

Next.js frontend for Sentiment Curator project.

## Setup

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Or use pnpm/yarn
pnpm install
yarn install
```

## Run

```bash
# Development server
npm run dev

# Or use the start script from project root
cd ..
.\start_dev.ps1
```

## Build

```bash
# Production build
npm run build

# Start production server
npm start
```

## Shadcn/UI Components

This project uses [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/) for components.

To add components:
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
npx shadcn@latest add card
# etc.
```
